38:06.800 --> 38:08.900
What was it?

38:08.900 --> 38:10.967
Remarkably similar to Phyliss
McGee.

38:10.967 --> 38:13.067
Phyliss McGee, the dead
grandmother?

38:13.067 --> 38:14.867
Come on now. What are you
saying?

38:14.867 --> 38:18.967
We got three dead bodies. All
