dressed like the grandmother.

38:31.267 --> 38:33.533
Are you gonna write about this?

38:33.533 --> 38:35.600
I'll have to.

38:35.600 --> 38:39.533
I guess you do.

38:39.533 --> 38:43.933
It's OK. I understand. I know
