38:48.133 --> 38:52.367
Sam was home all the time. He
never left the house.

38:52.367 --> 38:54.300
He must have been in the wrong
place at the wrong time.

38:54.300 --> 38:56.633
Uncle Gary didn't kill Sam.

38:56.633 --> 39:00.700
