42:15.067 --> 42:16.267
Wait a second. Don't talk to me
like that.

42:16.267 --> 42:17.833
I run the show here

42:17.833 --> 42:19.233
and I'll talk to you as I
please.

42:19.233 --> 42:21.100
You got that? I'm not some
walking hard on

42:21.100 --> 42:25.133
like some of these writers out
there on the floor that drool
whenever you walk by.

42:25.133 --> 42:27.167
You're a distraction Britney.

42:27.167 --> 42:29.200
What do you want me to do, wear
a bag over my head?

42:29.200 --> 42:33.067
No. What I want you to do is go
home. I'm done with you.

42:33.067 --> 42:35.300
And why is that?

42:35.300 --> 42:37.367
Um, mostly, because you annoy
me,

42:37.367 --> 42:39.367
but you're also coming onto a
married man.

42:39.367 --> 42:41.400
What are you, the morality
police?

42:41.400 --> 42:45.233
No, I run this paper and you're
gone.

42:45.233 --> 42:49.533
You're going to learn young
lady that bad things can happen
to bad girls.

42:49.533 --> 42:53.600
Very bad things.

42:53.600 --> 42:57.633
