43:22.067 --> 43:26.167
Do you like me? What?

43:26.167 --> 43:30.333
I'm a real good fuck. I can
fuck all night long.

43:30.333 --> 43:32.167
Get lost before I call the god
damn police.

43:32.167 --> 43:34.400
Come on bitch.

43:34.400 --> 43:36.300
Put out!

43:36.300 --> 43:38.600
Help! Somebody help me!

43:38.600 --> 43:42.800
We can share her!

43:42.800 --> 43:44.933
You sick fucking bastard.

43:44.933 --> 43:46.867
What? are you a homosexual?

43:46.867 --> 43:51.367
